Hello! My name is Sarah, and I represent RT 6 Boozers. How may I assist you today?

Hi Sarah! I have some questions about your happy hour specials.

Of course! I’d be happy to help you with that. May I ask your name, please?

My name is Jessica.

Thank you, Jessica! We appreciate you reaching out. Our happy hour runs from five to seven PM.

That sounds great! Are there any drink specials during that time?

Yes, we offer twenty-five percent off on all cocktails and beers during happy hour.

Awesome! Could you also tell me if I need to provide my identification?

Yes, we require one valid form of identification. Could you please provide me with your date of birth?

Sure, it is April tenth, nineteen eighty-five.

Thank you, and may I also get your phone number for our records?

Of course! It is five five five, one two three, four five six seven.

Thank you so much, Jessica! I appreciate your time. If you have any further questions, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
